         <critic>Scott Tobias</critic>
      </review>
      <review>
         <snippet>Director Goldmann, who cut his teeth directing videos for Shania Twain and Faith Hill, never misses a chance to punch-up an emotional scene with a contrived, heart-melting music performance by one or more of his stars.</snippet>
